{
  "info": {
    "name": "SpecQQ Chatbot Router API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for SpecQQ Chatbot Router System v1.0.0\n\nThis collection includes all 41 API endpoints organized by category:\n- Authentication (5 endpoints)\n- CQ Code Parsing (6 endpoints)\n- Statistics (4 endpoints)\n- Rules Management (7 endpoints)\n- Group Management (6 endpoints)\n- Message Logs (5 endpoints)\n- WebSocket (2 endpoints)\n- Health & Metrics (6 endpoints)\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Import the environment file (SpecQQ-API.postman_environment.json)\n3. Run the 'Login' request first to obtain JWT token\n4. Token is automatically stored in environment variable and used for all subsequent requests\n\n**Authentication:**\nAll requests (except Login and Init Admin) require JWT Bearer token.\nToken expires after 24 hours.\n\n**Base URL:**\n- Development: http://localhost:8080/api\n- Production: Update {{base_url}} in environment\n\n**Version**: 1.0.0\n**Last Updated**: 2026-02-11",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "specqq-v1"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Store JWT token in environment variable",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token_expires_in', jsonData.data.expiresIn);",
                  "    console.log('JWT token stored successfully');",
                  "    console.log('Token expires in: ' + jsonData.data.expiresIn + ' seconds');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "// Validate response",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response contains access token', function() {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('accessToken');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('tokenType');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.tokenType).to.eql('Bearer');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{admin_username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Authenticate user and obtain JWT token.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- username: Admin username (default: admin)\n- password: Admin password (default: admin123)\n\n**Response:**\n- accessToken: JWT token (valid for 24 hours)\n- tokenType: Bearer\n- expiresIn: Token expiration time in seconds (86400)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Info",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response contains user info', function() {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('username');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('role');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/user-info",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "user-info"]
            },
            "description": "Get current authenticated user information.\n\n**Requires:** JWT Bearer token\n\n**Response:**\n- username: User's username\n- role: User's role (ADMIN)\n- permissions: List of permissions"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('jwt_token', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('JWT token refreshed successfully');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Refresh JWT token before expiration.\n\n**Requires:** Valid JWT Bearer token\n\n**Response:**\n- accessToken: New JWT token\n- expiresIn: New expiration time"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('jwt_token');",
                  "    console.log('Logged out successfully, token cleared');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout and invalidate JWT token.\n\n**Requires:** JWT Bearer token\n\n**Effect:** Token is added to blacklist and cannot be reused"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
